We offer rental of hotels, hostels, and apartments (Apartamentos) in Calpe, Costa Blanca, Spain.
Calpe is a pearl by the sea between Valencia and Alicante.
We maintain order and thoroughly clean all our freshly renovated rooms (check out the reviews links below!).
Our well-priced hostels have everything for a comfortable stay:
- 5-minute walking distance to the sea, located in Calpe downtown (just near Sol y Mar hotel, Bahia hotel, Suitopia hotel)
- private shower and toilet
- air conditioning
- Wi-Fi
- safe
- electronic lock
- iron

The best location in Calp city center guarantees the maximum concentration of shops, restaurants, museums, galleries, and authentic streets.